        "subtopic": "Basic Rules",
        "content": "1. a^m × a^n = a^(m+n)\n2. a^m ÷ a^n = a^(m−n)\n3. (a^m)^n = a^(mn)\n4. a^0 = 1 (a ≠ 0)\n5. a^(−m) = 1 / a^m\n6. a^(1/n) = n-th root of a\n\n**Example:**\n2^3 × 2^4 = 2^7 = 128"
